column5: a friend of mine booked a cottage near sprucedale and was wondering if anyone has any information on the lake. Bartlett/rainy lake just north of huntsville. we are there for 5 days next week and have heard there are pike walleye and rainbow trout in the lake. to me it sounds like an odd combo of fish. any info will be greatly appreciated. thanks, Dan.
no rainbows.  not bad for the other two.
